	<screenshot>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/NK-IT-CLOUD/x2mail/main/img/screenshot-wizard.png</screenshot>
	<description><![CDATA[**X2Mail — Feature-rich webmail client for Nextcloud with native Single Sign-On support via XOAUTH2 and OAUTHBEARER.**

Works with Keycloak, Authentik, and any OpenID Connect provider. Powered by SnappyMail engine.

- **Native XOAUTH2/OAUTHBEARER support**
- **Auto token refresh for seamless SSO**
- **Works with user_oidc and oidc_login**
- **Dark mode and responsive design**
- **Full Sieve filtering support**
- **Integration with Nextcloud** (Contacts, Files, Calendar, Unified Search)
- **Multiple mail accounts and identities**
- **OpenPGP and S/MIME encryption**
	]]></description>
